  <brief_title>Outcome After Treatment of Pulmonary Aspergilloma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Outcome After Surgical Treatment or Bronchial Embolisation in Aspergilloma of the Lung: a Single Center Experience.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
